RQ2: Pre-registration anonymous traces

Here we review the pre-registration traces of volunteers who we were able to link anonymous traces to their user accounts. There are 1571 volunteers who contributed anonymously before registering for an account. On average there were 9.4131127 and a standard deviation of 14.1701869 events, including classifying. Removing classifying events there were on average 0.4850414 and a standard deviation of 1.6990815 events.
